XStringResourceDetails.Value: “Supply lines are a key factor to providing equipment to frontline forces. The enemy doesn’t seem to think they are that important though. Let’s see the cause and effect of disabling one of their main supply lines. Take away the workmen’s tools while they are out to lunch, be quick though, they’ll be back soon!”
XStringResourceDetails.Name: WXFE.MissionBriefing

XStringResourceDetails.Value: All explosive weapons do increased damage and will throw worms further than usual.
